222
00:22:46,908 --> 00:22:47,939
Us?

223
00:23:30,576 --> 00:23:32,230
Chuan Yu. It's both of us.

224
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:36,996
Chuan Yu is shy.

225
00:24:00,563 --> 00:24:01,659
Everyone,

226
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:04,115
you've been

227
00:24:04,402 --> 00:24:06,002
going through the difficult days with me

228
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:07,996
and you've turned them into good days.

229
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,342
I thank all of you

230
00:24:10,406 --> 00:24:12,926
for putting in so much effort to
celebrate my birthday with me.

231
00:24:13,519 --> 00:24:15,755
I, He Wei Fang, am very fortunate

232
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,200
to meet all of you in my life.

233
00:24:28,706 --> 00:24:29,835
I'll make it short.

234
00:24:30,553 --> 00:24:31,581
Anyway,

235
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:35,040
I'm grateful to all of you
for accompanying me.

236
00:24:37,788 --> 00:24:38,906
Thank you.

237
00:24:41,314 --> 00:24:42,422
That's not right.

238
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:44,396
Isn't this a surprise for Mu Dan?

239
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:45,880
