Mu Dan's bad drawing.

242
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:55,920
She spent a few nights drawing them.

243
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,343
Her hands are almost broken.

244
00:24:58,087 --> 00:24:59,113
Young Master.

245
00:24:59,559 --> 00:25:01,080
You suggested this plan

246
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:03,196
