247
00:25:04,279 --> 00:25:06,035
What did Mu Dan do

248
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,476
to make you reveal everything?

249
00:25:13,221 --> 00:25:14,303
Talk.

250
00:25:15,039 --> 00:25:16,439
